channel.title: Help! Can't get Cheezscape and Moparscape to work togethere!
channel.description:
I get my no-ip up and running, and I have the java thing working and stuff but, it never works. I log on and no updates are there.
Yes, I do put in the no-ip ip not the local address.
Do you have to put the no-ip ip somewhere in Cheezscape Client or Sever script?

item.title: Help! Can't get Cheezscape and Moparscape to work togethere!
item.dc:creator: @lothy Lothy
item.description:
@lothy wrote:

You can’t connect to yourself via the no-ip… You can only connect locally using the local address.

Read full topic
